DB is hosted on compass

During development everyone will run local server and react but use global database

4 Part series explaining the basics of the MERN stack

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qvBZevK1HPo&ab_channel=CodingTheSmartWay.com

When implementing a new feature create a branch on git, when it works publish to main on git

When main is updated everyone will have to pull from git